OL,3,CFind out how 'talking signs' are
OL,4,Ckeeping an island language alive
OL,6,FIt is hoped that the signs will make
OL,7,FJerriais more accessible and Laurence
OL,8,Fbelieves that there has been a recent
OL,9,Frevival of interest in the language,
OL,10,Falthough he admits it is very
OL,11,Fdifficult to hear the language being
OL,12,Fspoken.
OL,14,FHe adds: "I hope that the recordings
OL,15,Fwill help bring Jerriais to people who
OL,16,Fmight not otherwise hear it and
OL,17,Fperhaps inspire some of them to start
OL,18,Flearning."
